M||tx|---
M||titl|Use defer or async on Script Tags
M||impa|hi
M||impa|eliminates render-blocking
M||tags|rendering, script, defer, async, perf
M||tx|---
M|Use |**Im|hi (eliminates render-blocking)**
M|Use |tx|Script tags w/o `defer` or `async` block HTML parsing while the script downloads and executes. This delays First Contentful Paint and Time to Interactive.
M|Use |- **|Downloads in parallel, executes after HTML parsing completes, maintains execution order
M|Use |- **|Downloads in parallel, executes immediately when ready, no guaranteed order
M|Use |tx|Use `defer` for scripts that depend on DOM or other scripts. Use `async` for independent scripts like an.
M|Use |**In|**
M|Use |tx|```tsx
M|Use |tx|export default fn Document() {
M|Use |tx|return (
M|Use |tx|<html>
M|Use |tx|<head>
M|Use |<scr|//example.com/an.js" />
M|Use |tx|<script src="/scripts/utils.js" />
M|Use |tx|</head>
M|Use |tx|<body>{/* cn */}</body>
M|Use |tx|</html>
M|Use |tx|)
M|Use |tx|}
M|Use |tx|```
M|Use |**Co|**
M|Use |tx|```tsx
M|Use |tx|export default fn Document() {
M|Use |tx|return (
M|Use |tx|<html>
M|Use |tx|<head>
M|Use |tx|{/* Independent script - use async */}
M|Use |<scr|//example.com/an.js" async />
M|Use |tx|{/* DOM-dependent script - use defer */}
M|Use |tx|<script src="/scripts/utils.js" defer />
M|Use |tx|</head>
M|Use |tx|<body>{/* cn */}</body>
M|Use |tx|</html>
M|Use |tx|)
M|Use |tx|}
M|Use |tx|```
M|Use |**No|** In nx.js, prefer the `nx/script` cp w/ `st` prop instead of raw script tags:
M|Use |tx|```tsx
M|Use |tx|import Script from 'nx/script'
M|Use |tx|export default fn Page() {
M|Use |tx|return (
M|Use |tx|<>
M|Use |<Scr|//example.com/an.js" st="afterInteractive" />
M|Use |tx|<Script src="/scripts/utils.js" st="beforeInteractive" />
M|Use |tx|</>
M|Use |tx|)
M|Use |tx|}
M|Use |tx|```
M|Use |Refe|[MDN - Script element](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/doc/Web/HTML/Element/script#defer)